        indicated, home health <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">visitors</ENAMEX> followed up all patients
        similarly. The <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">third</NUMEX> potential limitation is that serum β 
        <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">2</NUMEX> microglobulin levels have not been
